successes.title: Travail: Democratizing Fine Dining in Robbinsdale, MN
successes.description: We have a vision for eating nirvana and we need your help to build it. #PrevailTravail

Pledges.description: FAMILY MEMBER: Thanks for supporting us! As one of our awesome backers, your name will be inscribed on our Family Wall inside the new Travail.

SOCIALITE: You never miss a good shindig, so you'll receive one spot at our official Prevailed Party hosted by James, Mike, Bob and Kale + your name inscribed on our Family Wall inside the new Travail.

ART AFICIONADO: You obviously appreciate the finer things, so you'll receive our irresistible 2014 Travail Sexy Chef Calendar (makes a great holiday gift!) + your name on our Family Wall + TWO spots at our Prevailed Party.

TREND SETTER: You like to be first, so you’ll receive one ticket for dinner during the new Travail’s special soft opening (meal included, but not alcohol—Kickstarter's rules, not ours) + your name on our Family Wall + two spots at our Prevailed Party + our spectacular 2014 Travail Sexy Chef Calendar.

ABOVE THE LINE: You don’t like waiting, so you’ll get to jump the line TWICE in 2014! That’s two separate reservations at a place that doesn’t do reservations + your name on our Family Wall + two spots at our Prevailed Party + our tempting 2014 Travail Sexy Chef Calendar + two tickets for dinner during the new Travail’s special soft opening (meal included, but not alcohol—Kickstarter's rules, not ours).

STAR APPRENTICE: Adult education is a wonderful thing (especially when you can eat your homework), so you’ll get TWO spots in a cooking class taught by James, Mike, Bob, and Kale (these will be scheduled on Sundays in 2014) + TWO signature blue Travail aprons (school uniform) + your name on our Family Wall + two spots at our Prevailed Party + our enchanting 2014 Travail Sexy Chef Calendar + two tickets for dinner during the new Travail’s special soft opening (meal included, but not alcohol—Kickstarter's rules, not ours) + TWO chances to jump the line in 2014

VIP: You enjoy being the center of attention, so you’ll get dinner for SIX at our big new Kitchen Table (meal included, but not alcohol—Kickstarter's rules, not ours) + your name on our Family Wall + SIX spots at our Prevailed Party + our phenomenal 2014 Travail Sexy Chef Calendar + two tickets for dinner during the new Travail’s special soft opening (again, meal included, but not alcohol) + FOUR chances to jump the line in 2014.

BALLER: You don’t do lines, we get that, so you’ll get a FULL YEAR of jumping the line in 2014 + your name on our Family Wall + six spots at our Prevailed Party + our volcanic 2014 Travail Sexy Chef Calendar + two tickets for dinner during the new Travail’s special soft opening (meal included, but not alcohol—Kickstarter's rules, not ours) + TWO dinners for six at our big new Kitchen Table (again, meal included, but not alcohol).   What the heck, we are throwing in TWO SPOTS at our cooking class and we dress you up with blue Travail aprons too!

TRAVAILIAN ROYALTY: La Di Da Di, you get a PRIVATE PARTY at Travail for up to 40 people on a Sunday, Monday, during July, or over our holiday break when we are closed to the public (all food, tip, and tax included, but not alcohol—Kickstarter's rules, not ours) + your name on our Family Wall + six spots at our Prevailed Party + our fierce 2014 Travail Sexy Chef Calendar + two tickets for dinner during the new Travail’s special soft opening (again, meal included, but not alcohol).   We suppose you want access to the cooking classes too, so sure we will get you two blue Travail aprons and 2 spots in the class!
